&lt;p data-start=&quot;955&quot; data-end=&quot;1126&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re a strong negotiator who enjoys analyzing market trends, building supplier relationships, and driving profitable purchasing decisions, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
